      "text": "Bet ja tas KUNGS twee-\nnu jaunn Leetu darrihs / un ta\nSemme favun Mutti atdarrihs /\num norih̄s tohs / ar wiſſu / kas\nteem peederr / ka tee dſihwi Ellê\nnogrimſt / tad juhs atſihfeet / ka\nſchee Zilweki to KUNGU irr ap-\nkaitinaſcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke / kad wiſſch\npabeidsis bij wiſſus schohs Wahr-\ndus ruunaht / tad pahrschkehlahs\nta Semme / kas appakſch wiſſ-\nneem bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Semme atdarrija\nfavun Mutti / um norihje tohs ar\nwiſſen Nainmeem / un wiſſeem\nZilwekeem / kas pee Korus bija /\num ar wiſſu wiſſaa Mantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee nogrimme / un\nwiſſ / kas teem peederreja / dſih-\nwi Ellê / un ta Semme apklahe\ntohs / un tee gahje bohjâ no tahs\nDraudses Starpas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Israëlitexi / kas\napkahrt wiſſeem bija / behdse\npreeſſch winno Brehkschann / jo\ntee fazztja : ka jafchu ta Semme\nmuhs arrf ne aprihj.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no ta KUNGA iſgah-\nje Ugguns / un aprihje tohs diwi-\nhints un peezdefmits Wihrus /\nkas tahs Kivehpja-Sahles up-\npureja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS runnaja\nus Mohsu / un fazztja :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Saffi us Eeleasaru / Ad-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo scho Grehzineeku Trau-\nki irr ſwehtiti zaar winno Dweh-\nſelehm / ka tee tohp par plaſka-\nneim Gabbaleem kalti / un palahr-\nti ap to Altari / jo tee irr uppu-\nreti preeſſch ta KUNGA / un\nſwehtiti / un teem buhs teem I-\nsraëka Behrneem par Siſmi\nbuht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Eleazars tas\nPreeſteris tohs warra Kwehpia-\nTraukus / fo tee Sadedſinati bij\npeeneſſſchi / un fitte tohs Plah-\ntis / par weenn Pahrwelkamu\npreeſſch to Altari.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Par Peeminneschann teem\nIsraëka Behrneem / ka ne weens\nSwefch / kas newa no Aâroṇa\nDsimmuma / pee-eetu kwehpinaht\nar Kwehpja-Sahlehn preeſſch to\nKUNGU : Ka taim ne notiktu / itt\nka Korum / un ka winna Puliam /\nittin ka tas KUNGS tam run-\nnajis bij zaar Mohsu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ohtrâ Deenâ furne-\nja wiſſa Israëta Behrnu Drau-\ndse prett Mohsu / un prett Aâro-\nnu / un fazztja : Juhs effat ta\nKUNGA Landis nokawſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad ta Draudse favul-\nzejahs prett Mohsu / un prett Aâ-\nronu greesahs tee us to Sa-ee-\nfchamas Telti / un raugi / tad ap-\nklahe to ta Padebbes / un ta\nKUNGA Godiba rahdijahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze Mohsus un\nPp 2 Aâ-\n"
    }
